window.bookSummaryJSON = "If it appears that you have everything, whether it be a beautiful home, an adoring family, and fulfilling work, why do you secretly harbor a desire for something more? Sarah Ban Breathnach, the wise, warm, and compassionate voice of <i>Simple Abundance</i>, takes you on a journey of self-discovery. Sarah encourages you to become an archaeologist of your Self: to plumb your past with its unfulfilled longings, forgotten pleasures, and abandoned dreams, to \"excavate\" the authentic woman buried inside. Assisting your personal \"dig\" will be hints and prompts from the lives of real women, including various celebrities. These anecdotes, in tandem with Sarah's personal insights, will help you unravel your own mystery and recover the joy that has been missing from your life. Along the way, you will experience small but exquisite epiphanies that will help you come to terms with your past choices and reveal exciting new opportunities that lead to your true destiny."; 
